ICTSD, ‘EU, Mercosur talks struggling to stay alive’, <i>Bridges Weekly Trade News Digest</i>, Vol. 15, No. 23, 22 June 2011<br/>

<a href="http://ictsd.org/i/news/bridgesweekly/109153/" target="_self">http://ictsd.org/i/news/bridgesweekly/109153/</a><br/>
